00059 //
00060 // calls from Compiler to VM
00061 //
00062 //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
00063 // Constant pool resolution
00064 //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
00065 //
00066 // The following byte codes reference constant pool entries:
00067 //
00068 //  field
00069 //      getstatic           static field
00070 //      putstatic           static field
00071 //      getfield            non-static field
00072 //      putfield            non-static field
00073 //
00074 //  method
00075 //      invokevirtual       virtual method
00076 //      invokespecial       special method
00077 //      invokestatic        static method
00078 //      invokeinterface     interface method
00079 //
00080 //  class
00081 //      new                 class
00082 //      anewarray           class
00083 //      checkcast           class
00084 //      instanceof          class
00085 //      multianewarray      class
00086 //
00087 
00088 //
00089 // For the method invocation byte codes, certain linkage exceptions are thrown 
00090 // at run-time:
00091 //
00092 //  (1) invocation of a native methods throws the UnsatisfiedLinkError if the 
00093 //      code that implements the method cannot be loaded or linked.
00094 //  (2) invocation of an interface method throws 
00095 //          - IncompatibleClassChangeError if the object does not implement 
00096 //            the called method, or the method is implemented as static
00097 //          - IllegalAccessError if the implemented method is not public
00098 //          - AbstractMethodError if the implemented method is abstract
00099 //
00100 
00101 VMEXPORT Field_Handle
00102 resolve_field(Compile_Handle h, Class_Handle c, unsigned index);
